<p>I have a requirement to transform the XML format of the SSRS report while exporting. I tried with some XSLT to implement this, but not getting desried output. </p>  <p>Default XML format of my report is</p>  <pre><code>&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;    &lt;Report xsi:schemaLocation="Test http://reportserver?    %2FTest&amp;amp;rs%3AFormat=XML&amp;amp;rc%3ASchema=True" Name="Test" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="Test"&gt;   &lt;Tablix1&gt;   &lt;Details_Collection&gt;   &lt;Details Country="India" Sales="1000.0000" /&gt;   &lt;/Details_Collection&gt;   &lt;/Tablix1&gt; &lt;/Report&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Output Needed (Report Tag is removed and the look and feel should be changed as below):</p>  <pre><code>&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;  &lt;Tablix1&gt; &lt;Details_Collection&gt; &lt;Details&gt;     &lt; Country&gt;"India"&lt;/COuntry&gt;      &lt;Sales&gt;1000.0000&lt;/Sales&gt; &lt;/Details&gt;  &lt;/Details_Collection&gt; &lt;/Tablix1&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Br,</p>  <p>Shamsuddeen</p>